00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:12.080
Who said Yu was timid?

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:19.840
Yu is truly the bravest child.

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:34.049
You ungrateful son!

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:39.299
Yu killed her and took her eyes
for his lover.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:40.520
Such affection

00:08:40.760 --> 00:08:42.200
is truly touching.

00:08:46.040 --> 00:08:47.960
You forced him to do that!

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.600
Yu did it himself.

00:08:51.640 --> 00:08:53.300
What does it have to do with me?

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:54.920
But

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:56.840
I am quite soft-hearted.

00:08:58.160 --> 00:08:59.760
Let's just consider

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:00.520
what happened today

00:09:00.520 --> 00:09:02.080
as a little secret.

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:05.040
Prime Minister Bai will still be

00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:07.240
the most powerful official in Mocheng.

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:09.760
Whether Feng Li returns or not,

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:11.000
you know,

00:09:12.040 --> 00:09:13.120
the Phoenix Seal

00:09:13.560 --> 00:09:15.490
will eventually end up in my hands.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.160
She actually came to Xiqi openly

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:46.650
under the pretext of a marriage alliance.

00:09:48.280 --> 00:09:49.560
Back in Mocheng,

00:09:49.560 --> 00:09:51.040
she was a bold, reckless,

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:52.970
and unpredictable vicious woman.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.520
I'm afraid this time,

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:56.460
she came with no good intentions.

00:09:58.440 --> 00:09:59.560
It seems this time,

00:09:59.800 --> 00:10:01.930
it'll be hard for us to get any benefit.

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:06.080
No matter how arrogant she was in Mocheng,

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:08.040
now that she's in Xiqi,

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:08.100
I'd like to see

00:10:08.100 --> 00:10:09.040
[Xiqi's Young Master, Xin Miao]

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:11.040
what kind of trouble she can stir up.

00:10:18.360 --> 00:10:20.020
Given my physical condition,

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:21.000
it's not convenient for me

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.730
to sleep with Mocheng's queen.

00:10:23.100 --> 00:10:23.240
[Xiqi's Young Master, Xin Yao]

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:24.520
You'll have to

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:26.880
put on the show tonight personally.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:28.600
Can you handle it?

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:31.680
We have collaborated for many years.

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:35.120
Why fear a woman?

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:50.730
We've arrived at Young Master's Mansion!

00:10:55.240 --> 00:10:56.500
Please, Your Majesty.

00:10:57.280 --> 00:10:58.520
Young Master has been

00:10:58.760 --> 00:11:00.560
eagerly awaiting your arrival.

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:19.210
Please wait, Your Majesty.

00:11:19.560 --> 00:11:20.800
This is not Mocheng.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:23.000
We have our own rules in Xiqi.

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:25.440
Before anyone
enters Young Master's Mansion,

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:27.200
they must be thoroughly searched

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:30.200
to prevent anyone
from carrying weapons into the mansion.

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.400
According to the mansion's rules,

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:32.520
before the wedding ceremony is completed,

00:11:32.520 --> 00:11:35.050
the bride
can't see Young Master's true face.

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:36.880
Therefore, before entering,

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.000
Your Majesty, please

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:39.040
cover your eyes.

00:11:39.920 --> 00:11:40.840
Do not disobey.

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:45.860
The young master of Xiqi truly...

00:11:47.840 --> 00:11:49.440
has many tricks.

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:00.920
Your Majesty,

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:02.730
you haven't been searched yet.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.430
[Mansion of Xiqi's Young Master]

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:20.400
Do you see clearly now?

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:24.840
This woman

00:12:25.200 --> 00:12:27.240
truly has no sense of shame at all.

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:40.440
It's so quiet in the mansion.

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:44.160
It's a joyous occasion,
but I don't hear any voice.

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:45.760
Is your young master

00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:47.840
welcoming a bride

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:49.260
or summoning a spirit?

00:12:49.520 --> 00:12:50.760
