00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:53.490
Young Master
has always preferred tranquility.

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:09.280
I can only escort you this far.

00:13:09.280 --> 00:13:10.160
Young Master has never

00:13:10.160 --> 00:13:12.020
allowed others to enter his room.

00:13:12.600 --> 00:13:13.860
Please, Your Majesty.

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:15.880
Thank you.

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:43.080
On the wedding night,
Young Master of Xiqi,

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:44.740
you prepared this hot spring.

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:47.640
Do you want to strip me bare

00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:49.490
and examine me closely?

00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:51.760
My wife

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:56.080
will be the most noble woman in Xiqi.

00:13:56.600 --> 00:13:58.360
She must be pure and untainted.

00:13:58.600 --> 00:14:00.400
She can't be a filthy woman.

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:10.330
Young Master, you really know how to jest.

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:12.520
Your wife

00:14:13.160 --> 00:14:15.840
is already the most noble woman.

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:19.560
Since you showed great sincerity,

00:14:19.640 --> 00:14:22.700
seeking to marry a royal lady
from Mocheng repeatedly,

00:14:23.400 --> 00:14:24.360
I will certainly

00:14:24.880 --> 00:14:27.240
grant you the same respect.

00:14:47.280 --> 00:14:48.440
The queen of Mocheng

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:50.580
truly lives up to her reputation.

00:14:55.800 --> 00:14:57.330
The young master of Xiqi...

00:14:59.640 --> 00:15:01.080
is also indeed...

00:15:03.080 --> 00:15:05.740
someone
who never shows his true face to others.

00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:08.040
It's hard to tell if you're real.

00:15:09.040 --> 00:15:10.520
This is Xiqi.

00:15:11.640 --> 00:15:13.600
How dare you doubt me?

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:16.160
No one

00:15:16.160 --> 00:15:18.360
has ever seen Young Master's true face.

00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:20.720
Then who knows

00:15:21.480 --> 00:15:23.120
if you are

00:15:24.120 --> 00:15:25.720
the real Young Master Yao?

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:41.930
Your Majesty, don't be impatient.

00:15:48.640 --> 00:15:50.080
As husband and wife,

00:15:50.440 --> 00:15:52.200
we are about...

00:15:56.520 --> 00:15:59.280
to meet each other with sincerity.